properties.name: detour6
properties.description: Detour #6: Marathon miles 9, 10 and 11: east of Park Blvd From 8:25am to 10:45am: Travel down Park Blvd, get on I-580 eastbound at Beaumont Ave. To travel westbound, get on I-580 westbound at Park Blvd. Of special note:From 8:00am to 10:15am, Park Blvd. will be closed to through traffic in both directions at Highway 13. (Parishioners of Zion Lutheran are requested to come up Park Blvd. from Highway I-580) Vehicles coming down Joaquin Miller will be redirected to take right onto Mountain into Montclair Village or onto Highway 13 northbound. Vehicles will not be able to continue down Lincoln. For members of the Greek Cathedral of the Ascension or the Mormon Temple, vehicle traffic will be allowed down Joaquin Miller and into the parking lots ONLY. Traffic will be allowed up Lincoln from the east side of MacArthur Blvd. After 10:45am: Runners will have cleared area; streets will be reopened to normal traffic.
